# BMI Calculator (Dockerized)

A simple Node.js application that calculates Body Mass Index (BMI).  
This project demonstrates **basic Docker containerization** and **Continuous Integration (CI) using GitHub Actions**.

---

## 🚀 Features
- Calculate BMI using weight (kg) and height (m).  
- Error handling for invalid inputs.  
- Dockerized for easy deployment.  
- Continuous Integration pipeline runs tests automatically on each push.  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- **Node.js** (Express framework)  
- **Jest** (Unit Testing)  
- **Docker** (Containerization)  
- **GitHub Actions** (CI Pipeline)  

---

## 📦 Installation
Clone the repository and install dependencies:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/miracleify/CodeSentinel_BasicDocker-Containerization.git
cd CodeSentinel_BasicDocker-Containerization
npm install
